{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6281c3c700","title":"政务院关于1950年公粮征收决定","origin":"中国社会科学院、中央档案馆编：《中华人民共和国经济档案资料选编（财政卷）1949-1952》，北京：经济管理出版社，1995年[G128－1－1046]。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b6760244d9","index":0,"year":1950,"month":11,"day":27,"articleId":"6281c3c700"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bab7d2d8d2","type":"title","text":"政务院关于1950年公粮征收决定","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700"},{"id":"5451228a89","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700"},{"id":"be35c64ee1","type":"paragraph","text":"关于1950年公粮征收及附加，决定：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700"},{"id":"5ad34ad628","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）中央分配各区之公粮数字，其超过部分，应全部上解中央。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700"},{"id":"3a6af00f8c","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）公粮地方附加，一律提到30％，已征15％者，补征15％，已征20％者，补征10％，以解决地方部队的供给问题，并弥补地方开支的不足。计分配：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700"},{"id":"2c1d123625","type":"paragraph","text":"华东：6.75亿斤，其中应上解中央3.3亿斤。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700"},{"id":"8d4ff1ffe8","type":"paragraph","text":"中南：5.35亿斤，其中应上解中央3.6亿斤。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700"},{"id":"68059152fb","type":"paragraph","text":"西南：3.1亿斤，其中应上解中央2.1亿斤。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700"},{"id":"41edd5b816","type":"paragraph","text":"西北：1.2亿斤，其中应上解中央5000万斤。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700"},{"id":"8dda95c2e1","type":"paragraph","text":"华北：4.65亿斤，其中应上解中央2.1亿斤。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700"}],"page":{"id":"d424512c42","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6281c3c700","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}